text: Muraz Giorgadze (born June 28, 1994) is a Georgian Rugby Union player. His position is wing and he currently plays for Armazi in the Georgia Championship and the Georgia national team. ==References== Category:Rugby union players from Georgia (country) Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Tbilisi Category:1994 births Category:Rugby union locks Category:Georgia international rugby union players
